MakeSpecsBetter
===============

Tired of broken specs?
Need some help to get through the day?
Maybe, just maybe, MakeSpecsBetter can help youget through it.


Example
=======

ruby script/plugin install git://github.com/matthewrudy/MakeSpecsBetter

rake spec BETTER=true - "take away  your troubles"
rake spec:better      - "make your dreams come alive"
export BETTER=true    - "rake away the pain"

